# PhotographyCourses Virtual Camera 4.1

A structured production prototype containing:

- Interactive 3D camera
- Exposure and image-quality simulation
- Structured photography academy
- Timed challenges, scores, stars and achievements
- Browser-saved progress
- Photography coaching interface
- Spoken advice through browser speech synthesis

## Structure

```text
index.html
css/
js/
assets/
lessons/
docs/
```

Version 4.1 preserves the working Version 4 code while introducing a maintainable project structure and clear future module boundaries.

## Local testing

Run a local web server:

```bash
python -m http.server 8080
```

Then visit `http://localhost:8080`.

